{
  "Though creating a simple <code>Counter</code> app is <span class=\"font-black tracking-wider\" style=\"color:var(--blue)\">cool</span> and gives us a gentle introduction to <code>useState</code>, it's not <em metastring=\"\">super</em> practical. Let's look at some other use cases that'll give us more insight into how we can leverage <code>useState</code> in more scenarios.": "写一个简单的 <code>Counter</code> 应用<span class=\"font-black tracking-wider\" style=\"color:var(--blue)\">挺酷</span>，也让我们轻松入门了 <code>useState</code>，但它其实不<em metastring=\"\">太</em>实用。下面看几个别的用例，让我们更清楚地了解如何在更多场景里用好 <code>useState</code>。",
  "It's important to note that when you pass a value to <code>useState</code>'s updater function, whatever value you pass will always <strong metastring=\"\">replace</strong> the current piece of state.": "要特别注意：当你把一个值传给 <code>useState</code> 的更新函数时，不管传什么，它都会<strong metastring=\"\">替换</strong>当前这块 state。",
  "Instead of replacing the object, you most likely want to <strong metastring=\"\">merge</strong> the new value with the existing state object. To do that, we can use JavaScript's spread operator to spread all of the existing key/value pairs onto a new object, then pass that new object to the updater function.": "你大概率想要的不是替换整个对象，而是把新值<strong metastring=\"\">合并</strong>到已有的 state 对象上。做法是用 JavaScript 的展开运算符把现有的所有键值对展开到一个新对象里，然后再把这个新对象传给更新函数。",
  "At this point our app is progressing <del metastring=\"\">slowly</del> nicely. Unfortunately, it still doesn't resemble much of a todo <em metastring=\"\">list</em>.": "到这里，我们的应用<del metastring=\"\">慢慢</del>进展得不错。可惜它看起来还不太像一个 todo <em metastring=\"\">列表</em>。",
  "What if instead of having each <code>Todo</code> component manage its own state, we <span class=\"font-bold relative m-px\" style=\"bottom:0px\">l</span><span class=\"font-bold relative m-px\" style=\"bottom:1px\">i</span><span class=\"font-bold relative m-px\" style=\"bottom:2px\">f</span><span class=\"font-bold relative m-px\" style=\"bottom:3px\">t</span> that state up to the parent <code>TodoList</code> component?": "假如我们不让每个 <code>Todo</code> component 自己管理 state，而是把 state <span class=\"font-bold relative m-px\" style=\"bottom:0px\">提</span><span class=\"font-bold relative m-px\" style=\"bottom:1px\">升</span><span class=\"font-bold relative m-px\" style=\"bottom:2px\">上</span><span class=\"font-bold relative m-px\" style=\"bottom:3px\">去</span>到父组件 <code>TodoList</code> 会怎么样？",
  "This would solve all of our problems. <code>TodoList</code> would <em metastring=\"\">own</em> (and manage) the state of each todo item and then we can pass data down to components that need it via props.": "这样就能解决我们所有的问题。<code>TodoList</code> 会<em metastring=\"\">拥有</em>（并管理）每一个 todo 项的 state，我们再通过 props 把数据传给需要的子组件。",
  "The only gotcha is how you update that state. Often times when lifting state up, you decouple <em metastring=\"\">where</em> the state lives from the event handlers that update that state.": "唯一要注意的是：你怎么更新这个 state。往上提升 state 时，state 所在的位置往往和更新 state 的事件处理函数解耦开了。",
  "So first, let's <span class=\"font-bold relative m-px\" style=\"bottom:0px\">l</span><span class=\"font-bold relative m-px\" style=\"bottom:1px\">i</span><span class=\"font-bold relative m-px\" style=\"bottom:2px\">f</span><span class=\"font-bold relative m-px\" style=\"bottom:3px\">t</span> our <span class=\"ch-section-link\" data-active=\"false\">todo state</span> up to a new <code>TodoList</code> component and then pass it down via a prop to the <span class=\"ch-section-link\" data-active=\"false\">Todo</span> component.": "首先，我们把 <span class=\"ch-section-link\" data-active=\"false\">todo state</span> <span class=\"font-bold relative m-px\" style=\"bottom:0px\">提</span><span class=\"font-bold relative m-px\" style=\"bottom:1px\">升</span><span class=\"font-bold relative m-px\" style=\"bottom:2px\">上</span><span class=\"font-bold relative m-px\" style=\"bottom:3px\">去</span>到一个新的 <code>TodoList</code> component 里，然后通过 prop 往下传给 <span class=\"ch-section-link\" data-active=\"false\">Todo</span> component。",
  "First, we'll remove the local <code>todo</code> state and accept it as a <span class=\"ch-section-link\" data-active=\"false\">prop</span> since it now lives inside of the parent <span class=\"ch-section-link\" data-active=\"false\"><code>TodoList</code></span> component.": "首先，我们删掉本地的 <code>todo</code> state，改为把它作为 <span class=\"ch-section-link\" data-active=\"false\">prop</span> 接收 —— 因为它现在放在父组件 <span class=\"ch-section-link\" data-active=\"false\"><code>TodoList</code></span> 里了。",
  "Next, we'll update our event handlers to use our new <code>handleUpdateTodo</code> prop that we also passed down from the parent <span class=\"ch-section-link\" data-active=\"false\"><code>TodoList</code></span> component.": "接下来，我们更新事件处理函数，让它们使用从父组件 <span class=\"ch-section-link\" data-active=\"false\"><code>TodoList</code></span> 往下传的新 prop <code>handleUpdateTodo</code>。",
  "Notice that <code>handleUpdateTodo</code> has an <span class=\"ch-section-link\" data-active=\"false\"><code>updatedTodo</code></span> parameter. This is how we get data from where the event handlers live, in a child component, back up to where the state lives, in the parent component.": "注意 <code>handleUpdateTodo</code> 有一个 <span class=\"ch-section-link\" data-active=\"false\"><code>updatedTodo</code></span> 参数。事件处理函数住在子组件里，state 住在父组件里 —— 正是通过这个参数，我们把数据从子组件回传给父组件。",
  "It doesn't matter <em metastring=\"\">where</em> <code>handleUpdateTodo</code> is called, it just matters that when it's called, it receives this <code>updatedTodo</code> argument.": "<code>handleUpdateTodo</code> 在<em metastring=\"\">哪里</em>被调用并不重要，重要的是它被调用时能收到 <code>updatedTodo</code> 这个参数。",
  "So now inside of the child <code>Todo</code> component, we need to make sure when we invoke <span class=\"ch-section-link\" data-active=\"false\">handleUpdateTodo</span>, we pass it the updated todo item.": "所以在子组件 <code>Todo</code> 里，调用 <span class=\"ch-section-link\" data-active=\"false\">handleUpdateTodo</span> 时必须把更新后的 todo 项传过去。",
  "At this point our app is in better shape than it was before, but it's still not a todo <strong metastring=\"\">list</strong>. Let's fix that.": "到这里，应用状态比之前好了，但它还不是一个 todo <strong metastring=\"\">列表</strong>。我们来把这个补上。",
  "We'll do the same thing here by updating the state in our <code>TodoList</code> component to be an <em metastring=\"\">array</em> of todo objects, rather than just a single todo object.": "这里同样做一次类似的改动：把 <code>TodoList</code> component 里的 state 改成一个 todo 对象的<em metastring=\"\">数组</em>，而不是单个 todo 对象。",
  "Similar to objects, whenever you want to update an array that's on state, you need to pass the updater function a <strong metastring=\"\">new</strong> array which will replace the current array.": "和对象一样，每当你要更新 state 里的数组时，都要传给更新函数一个<strong metastring=\"\">新的</strong>数组，用它来替换当前的数组。",
  "In this case, because <code>TodoList</code> is the component that owns our <span class=\"ch-section-link\" data-active=\"false\"><code>todos</code></span> state, we'll want to create our function for deleting todo items in the same component.": "在这里，因为 <code>TodoList</code> 就是拥有 <span class=\"ch-section-link\" data-active=\"false\"><code>todos</code></span> state 的组件，我们就把删除 todo 项的函数放在同一个组件里写。",
  "Let's call it <code>handleDeleteTodo</code> and have it take in the <span class=\"ch-section-link\" data-active=\"false\"><code>id</code></span> of the todo item to delete as its only argument.": "我们叫它 <code>handleDeleteTodo</code>，它的唯一参数是要删除的 todo 项的 <span class=\"ch-section-link\" data-active=\"false\"><code>id</code></span>。",
  "Though it may have been... <span class=\"font-black tracking-wider\" style=\"color:var(--red)\">painstaking</span>, hopefully at this point you feel confident with <em metastring=\"\">all</em> aspects of managing state in React – including updating objects/array state as well as <span class=\"font-bold relative m-px\" style=\"bottom:0px\">l</span><span class=\"font-bold relative m-px\" style=\"bottom:1px\">i</span><span class=\"font-bold relative m-px\" style=\"bottom:2px\">f</span><span class=\"font-bold relative m-px\" style=\"bottom:3px\">t</span><span class=\"font-bold relative m-px\" style=\"bottom:4px\">i</span><span class=\"font-bold relative m-px\" style=\"bottom:5px\">n</span><span class=\"font-bold relative m-px\" style=\"bottom:6px\">g</span> state up.": "虽然过程可能有点<span class=\"font-black tracking-wider\" style=\"color:var(--red)\">磨人</span>，但希望到这里你对在 React 中管理 state 的<em metastring=\"\">所有</em>方面都已经心中有数 —— 包括更新 object/array 类型的 state，以及<span class=\"font-bold relative m-px\" style=\"bottom:0px\">提</span><span class=\"font-bold relative m-px\" style=\"bottom:1px\">升</span><span class=\"font-bold relative m-px\" style=\"bottom:2px\">状</span><span class=\"font-bold relative m-px\" style=\"bottom:3px\">态</span><span class=\"font-bold relative m-px\" style=\"bottom:4px\">向</span><span class=\"font-bold relative m-px\" style=\"bottom:5px\">上</span><span class=\"font-bold relative m-px\" style=\"bottom:6px\">传</span>。",
  "Learning when and how to <span class=\"font-bold relative m-px\" style=\"bottom:0px\">l</span><span class=\"font-bold relative m-px\" style=\"bottom:1px\">i</span><span class=\"font-bold relative m-px\" style=\"bottom:2px\">f</span><span class=\"font-bold relative m-px\" style=\"bottom:3px\">t</span> state up is one of the most important aspects of state management in React.": "学会<span class=\"font-bold relative m-px\" style=\"bottom:0px\">什</span><span class=\"font-bold relative m-px\" style=\"bottom:1px\">么</span><span class=\"font-bold relative m-px\" style=\"bottom:2px\">时</span><span class=\"font-bold relative m-px\" style=\"bottom:3px\">候</span>以及如何把 state 提升上去，是 React state 管理中最重要的方面之一。",
  "Here's the rule of thumb – whenever you have state that multiple components depend on, you'll want to <span class=\"font-bold relative m-px\" style=\"bottom:0px\">l</span><span class=\"font-bold relative m-px\" style=\"bottom:1px\">i</span><span class=\"font-bold relative m-px\" style=\"bottom:2px\">f</span><span class=\"font-bold relative m-px\" style=\"bottom:3px\">t</span> that state up to the nearest parent component and then pass it <span class=\"font-bold relative m-px\" style=\"bottom:3px\">d</span><span class=\"font-bold relative m-px\" style=\"bottom:2px\">o</span><span class=\"font-bold relative m-px\" style=\"bottom:1px\">w</span><span class=\"font-bold relative m-px\" style=\"bottom:0px\">n</span> via props.": "经验法则是：当多个组件都依赖同一块 state 时，就把这块 state <span class=\"font-bold relative m-px\" style=\"bottom:0px\">提</span><span class=\"font-bold relative m-px\" style=\"bottom:1px\">升</span><span class=\"font-bold relative m-px\" style=\"bottom:2px\">到</span><span class=\"font-bold relative m-px\" style=\"bottom:3px\">上</span>级最近的共同父组件里，然后通过 props <span class=\"font-bold relative m-px\" style=\"bottom:3px\">往</span><span class=\"font-bold relative m-px\" style=\"bottom:2px\">下</span><span class=\"font-bold relative m-px\" style=\"bottom:1px\">传</span><span class=\"font-bold relative m-px\" style=\"bottom:0px\">递</span>。",
  "Whenever you're in a situation like this, what you'll want to do is create a <span class=\"ch-section-link\" data-active=\"false\">function</span> in the component where the state is located, and then pass that function down via <span class=\"ch-section-link\" data-active=\"false\">props</span>.": "每当遇到这种情况，你应该在 state 所在的组件里创建一个 <span class=\"ch-section-link\" data-active=\"false\">函数</span>，然后通过 <span class=\"ch-section-link\" data-active=\"false\">props</span> 把这个函数往下传。",
  "Then, you can pass data back up to the parent component by passing an <span class=\"ch-section-link\" data-active=\"false\">argument</span> to the function you passed down.": "然后，你就可以给那个你往下传的函数传一个 <span class=\"ch-section-link\" data-active=\"false\">参数</span>，把数据再送回父组件。",
  "The biggest thing to notice is the relationship between <span class=\"ch-section-link\" data-active=\"false\">handleUpdateTodo</span> in the parent component, and <span class=\"ch-section-link\" data-active=\"false\">handleCheckboxClick</span> and <span class=\"ch-section-link\" data-active=\"false\">handleEditTodo</span> in the child component.": "最值得注意的，是父组件里的 <span class=\"ch-section-link\" data-active=\"false\">handleUpdateTodo</span> 与子组件里的 <span class=\"ch-section-link\" data-active=\"false\">handleCheckboxClick</span>、<span class=\"ch-section-link\" data-active=\"false\">handleEditTodo</span> 之间的关系。"
}